      "@id": "https://augmanitai.com/terms/AUG-0501",
      "name": "The Style Shifter",
      "description": "Die Faehigkeit, mit KI-Hilfe bewusst zwischen verschiedenen Schreibstilen zu wechseln und neue Stile zu erschliessen.",
      "inDefinedTermSet": "https://augmanitai.com/terms/periodic/",
      "termCode": "AUG-0501",
      "alternateName": "SSF",
      "inLanguage": "de",
      "about": "KM",
      "operationalDefinition": "Operational scope: an instance of 'The Style Shifter' is counted when the observable pattern described above (Die Faehigkeit, mit KI-Hilfe bewusst zwischen verschiedenen Schreibstilen zu wec...) occurs at least once within a defined interaction segment of N turns (typically N=10), as coded by trained raters.",
      "measurementSchema": "Coding-scheme occurrence count; observer agreement (Cohen's κ).",
      "exampleData": "{\"session_id\": \"S001\", \"occurrence_count\": 5, \"kappa\": 0.74}",
      "broader": "https://andreasehstandlicenseofclarityloc.github.io/augmanitai-periodic/#topic-communication-language",
      "inScheme": "https://andreasehstandlicenseofclarityloc.github.io/augmanitai-periodic/#topic-communication-language",
      "mainEntityOfPage": "https://andreasehstandlicenseofclarityloc.github.io/augmanitai-periodic/terms/AUG-0501.html",
      "citation": "https://zenodo.org/communities/augmanitai",
