      "operationalDefinition": "Operational scope: an instance of 'The Syntax Voice' is counted when the observable pattern described above (Neue Satzkonstruktionen und Ausdruecke werden Teil des eigenen sprachlichen Repe...) occurs at least once within a defined interaction segment of N turns (typically N=10), as coded by trained raters.",
      "measurementSchema": "Coding-scheme occurrence count; observer agreement (Cohen's κ).",
