      "name": "Platform Ontology",
      "description": "Jedes KI-System bringt eine eigene Perspektive mit, gepraegt durch Trainingsdaten und Architektur.",
      "inDefinedTermSet": "https://augmanitai.com/terms/periodic/",
      "termCode": "AUG-0006",
      "alternateName": "PLO",
      "inLanguage": "de",
      "about": "SY",
      "operationalDefinition": "Operational scope: an instance of 'Platform Ontology' is counted when the observable pattern described above (Jedes KI-System bringt eine eigene Perspektive mit, gepraegt durch Trainingsdate...) occurs at least once within a defined interaction segment of N turns (typically N=10), as coded by trained raters.",
      "measurementSchema": "Coding-scheme occurrence count; observer agreement (Cohen's κ).",
