      "termCode": "AUG-0915",
      "alternateName": "EMB",
      "inLanguage": "de",
      "about": "AG",
      "operationalDefinition": "Operational scope: an instance of 'Embodiment Effect' is counted when the observable pattern described above (Physische Praesenz eines KI-Systems veraendert die Interaktionsdynamik gegenuebe...) occurs at least once within a defined interaction segment of N turns (typically N=10), as coded by trained raters.",
      "measurementSchema": "Initiative-event count (AI-initiated actions per N turns); complementary indicator: override-rate.",
      "exampleData": "{\"session_id\": \"S001\", \"ai_initiative_count_per_10_turns\": 3, \"override_rate\": 0.10}",
      "broader": "https://andreasehstandlicenseofclarityloc.github.io/augmanitai-periodic/#topic-agentic-ai",
